description: Demolition of existing buildings and erection of a 39 storey residential building providing 302 residential units (Class C3) with flexible retail or caf / restaurant units (Class A1 or A3) at ground floor, a 10 storey business building providing office accomodation (Class B1) with flexible retail or caf / restaurant units (Class A1 or A3) at ground floor and a single storey flexible retail or caf / restaurant kiosk (Class A1 or A3), associated landscaping, car parking, vehicular access and cycle parking. Application accompanied by an Environmental Statement submitted pursuant to the Town and Country Planning (Environmental Impact Assessment) Regulations 2011.
